      "writtenOn": "2020-11-25T08:37:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How about\n\n```\nmessage CreateArtifactRequest {\n  Artifact artifact \u003d 1;\n  bytes content \u003d 2;\n  string content_hash \u003d 3;\n}\n\nmessage DownloadArtifactsResponse {\n  Artifact artifact \u003d 1;\n  bytes content \u003d 2;\n}\n```\n\nThen, field `content` appears in the request message of applicable RPCs only.",
