        "id": 1147264
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-25T08:37:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We currently use it to check a duplicate before computing the hash of the actual content.\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/resultdb/internal/services/recorder/create_artifact.go;l\u003d374",
      "parentUuid": "a402d172_4f54db56",
