      "writtenOn": "2020-11-25T16:44:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "in that code, we need the hash before starting streaming to RBE, but we don\u0027t have the hash until we finished reading the request body. There we have a choice of either buffering the contents, or asking the client to provide pre-computed hash. We do the latter.\n\nHere we don\u0027t have to do this because the content is already buffered.",
